==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: as if no one is by one's side
===Idiom===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' páng ruò wú rén, pang2ruo4wu2ren2)
# to selfishly do what one wants without regard to other people's wishes
